summaries.short: A customer's bike is stolen; a provocateur finds a new outlet.
summaries.full: After his bike is stolen, regular customer Marty consults The Guy, whose suggestion sends Marty down a surprising path. Bored with her mundane life, Darby finds various ways to unnerve and bewilder strangers.

summaries.full: Season Three Premiere. While spending some time in his RV and away from the city, The Guy gets some upsetting news but makes an intriguing new connection. Cori, meanwhile, is trying to adjust to a new reality without her friend.

summaries.short: A man strives for a life free of Internet distractions; a comedian is trolled after a tweet; a dancer attempts a world record.
summaries.full: Deciding to embrace a life without the distractions of the Internet, a computer programmer tries out a tech-free night per The Guy's advice. After a controversial tweet draws attention, a comedian becomes inundated by Internet trolls. While attempting to match a world record, a fearless dancer struggles as the hours drag on and her dance partners fall by the wayside.
